== 個人生活 ==
在[[曼徹斯特大學|曼徹斯特大學]]就讀時認識現為女演員的{{tsl|en|Olivia Poulet|Olivia Poulet}}，兩人交往逾10年，2005年甘巴貝治赴南非拍攝《{{tsl|en|To the Ends of The Earth|To the Ends of The Earth}}》前，兩人曾短暫分手，但其後甘巴貝治在南非遇上綁架，回國後兩人決定復合。不過最後兩人終於2011年再度分手。Olivia Poulet曾於《[[神探夏洛克|新福爾摩斯]]》第一季第二集中客串演出其中一名死者的秘書一角。<ref>{{Cite web |url= http://www.standard.co.uk/showbiz/starinterviews/benedict-cumberbatch--stepping-into-the-lead-6475519.html |title= Benedict Cumberbatch - stepping into the lead |author= Nick Curtis |date= 2010-06-01 |publisher= London Evening Standard |language=  |accessdate=  |quote=  |archive-date= 2015-07-17 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20150717032506/http://www.standard.co.uk/showbiz/starinterviews/benedict-cumberbatch--stepping-into-the-lead-6475519.html |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url= http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-1367189/Sherlock-Holmess-star-Benedict-Cumberbatch-splits-university-sweetheart-years.html |title= Sherlock Holmes' star Benedict Cumberbatch splits from university sweetheart after ten years together |author= RICHARD KAY |date= 2011-03-18 |publisher= Daily Mail |language=  |accessdate=  |quote=  |archive-date= 2016-03-04 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160304133758/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-1367189/Sherlock-Holmess-star-Benedict-Cumberbatch-splits-university-sweetheart-years.html |dead-url= no }}</ref>與 Olivia Poulet 分手後，曾跟時裝設計師 Anna James 短暫交往至2012年1月分手<ref>{{Cite web |url= http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/showbiz/news/a340015/benedict-cumberbatch-finds-new-girlfriend-anna-jones.html |title= Benedict Cumberbatch finds new girlfriend Anna Jones |author= Paul Millar |date= 2011-09-12 |publisher= Digital Spy |language=  |accessdate=  |quote=  |archive-date= 2015-10-15 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20151015025519/http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/showbiz/news/a340015/benedict-cumberbatch-finds-new-girlfriend-anna-jones.html |dead-url= no }}</ref>

2014年11月5日，甘巴貝治宣佈跟劇場導演{{link-en|蘇菲·亨特|Sophie Hunter}}訂婚，婚訊由甘巴貝治的父母以英國傳統方式，於《[[泰晤士报|泰吾士報]]》的婚訊版刊登宣告<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/benedict-cumberbatch-engagement-news-sends-746560?facebook_20141105 |title= Benedict Cumberbatch Engagement News Sends Twitter Ablaze |author= Alex Ritman |date=2014-11-05 |publisher= The Hollywood Reporter |language= |accessdate= |quote= }}</ref>。2015年2月14日，兩人於[[懷特島郡|懷特島郡]]上的{{link-en|聖伯多祿聖保祿堂|St. Peter and St. Paul's Church, Mottistone}}結婚。<ref>{{Cite web|url= http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/celebritynews/11414433/Are-Mr-and-Mrs-Cumberbatch-honeymooning-in-the-Isle-of-Wight.html|title= Are Benedict Cumberbatch and Sophie Hunter honeymooning in the Isle of Wight?|author= Camilla Turner|date= 2015-02-15|publisher= The Telegraph|language= |accessdate= |quote= |archive-date= 2019-06-29|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20190629122453/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/celebritynews/11414433/Are-Mr-and-Mrs-Cumberbatch-honeymooning-in-the-Isle-of-Wight.html|dead-url= no}}</ref>2015年6月1日，{{link-en|蘇菲·亨特|Sophie Hunter}}誕下跟甘巴貝治的首名孩子，取名為Christopher Carlton Cumberbatch<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.express.co.uk/celebrity-news/601741/Benedict-Cumberbatch-wife-Sophie-name-son-Christopher-Carlton |title=Benedict Cumberbatch and wife Sophie Hunter name baby son 'Christopher Carlton' |date=2015-08-30 |publisher=Daily Express |language= |accessdate= |quote= |archive-date=2021-01-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125095229/https://www.express.co.uk/celebrity-news/601741/Benedict-Cumberbatch-wife-Sophie-name-son-Christopher-Carlton |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2016年10月，甘巴貝治宣佈妻子懷有第二名孩子。<ref>{{Cite web |url= http://people.com/babies/benedict-cumberbatch-wife-sophie-hunter-pregnant-expecting-second-child/ |title= Benedict Cumberbatch’s Wife Sophie Hunter Is Pregnant: ‘Everyone Is Absolutely Thrilled’ |author= George Stark |date= 2016-10-21 |publisher= People |language=  |accessdate=  |quote=  |archive-date= 2018-07-05 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20180705233119/https://people.com/babies/benedict-cumberbatch-wife-sophie-hunter-pregnant-expecting-second-child/ |dead-url= no }}</ref>甘巴貝治為二兒子取名為Hal，全名為Hal Auden Cumberbatch，這個名字是來自於莎士比亞名劇《亨利四世》中將成為「亨利五世」的哈爾王子。

因母親的緣故，自幼便與在神探福爾摩斯中飾演Mrs. Hudson的女演員[[尤娜·斯塔布斯|尤娜·斯塔布斯]]相識，另外也認識以詮釋福爾摩斯聞名的英國演員[[杰里米·布雷特|杰里米·布雷特]]。<ref>{{Cite web |url= http://blogs.laweekly.com/squidink/2012/05/q_a_with_una_stubbs.php |title= Q & A With Una Stubbs: The Joy of Victoria Sponges + Getting Sherlock Holmes to Eat |author= Margy Rochlin |date= 2012-05-07 |publisher=  |language=  |accessdate=  |quote=  |archive-date= 2014-01-04 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20140104113636/http://blogs.laweekly.com/squidink/2012/05/q_a_with_una_stubbs.php |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref name="#1"/>

甘巴貝治曾兩次跟死神擦身而過。第一次是他入讀大學前於藏區僧院教導英文時的事。當時他跟4位朋友到尼泊爾遠足，由於食物和裝備不足，加上沒有請導遊，結果中途迷了路，他們要在夜間趕路，並於沼澤裏尋找水源，夜宿野獸的巢穴，為了走過結了冰的河流，更差點弄斷脖子。最後他們沿着氂牛糞的痕跡才找到人煙，甘巴貝治更因此而染上痢疾。<ref name="#2">{{Cite web |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/home/event/article-2314671/Star-Trek-returns-Benedict-Cumberbatch-boldly-goes-Sherlock-Trekkie.html |title=I'm definitely middle class...OK maybe I'm upper middle class': From Sherlock to Star Trek, Benedict Cumberbatch on his meteoric rise to stardom |author=Amy Raphael |date=2013-04-27 |publisher=The Daily Mail |language= |accessdate= |quote= |archive-date=2021-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126112458/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/home/event/article-2314671/Star-Trek-returns-Benedict-Cumberbatch-boldly-goes-Sherlock-Trekkie.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="#3">{{Cite web |url=http://www.gq-magazine.co.uk/entertainment/articles/2013-12/02/benedict-cumberbatch-gq-cover-sherlock/viewall |title=The many lives of Benedict Cumberbatch |author=Stuart McGurk |date=2013-12-31 |publisher=GQ Magazine(UK) |language= |accessdate= |quote= |archive-date=2014-10-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141013182918/http://www.gq-magazine.co.uk/entertainment/articles/2013-12/02/benedict-cumberbatch-gq-cover-sherlock/viewall |dead-url=no }}</ref>

另一次發生在2005年，甘巴貝治於南非拍攝《{{lang|en|To the Ends of The Earth}}》時，跟同劇的演員Denise Black及Theo Landey出遊，其間遇上了綁架事件。劫匪趁他們為汽車換胎時劫走他們，並要他們交出所有財物。甘巴貝治頭部受傷，被劫匪鎖在汽車行李箱內，其後被劫匪用槍械的指嚇，以被處決的姿勢跪在地下，最終在午夜時平安獲釋。甘巴貝治的手腕上因這次事件留下疤痕。<ref>{{Cite web |url= http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/tvandradio/9009080/Sherlock-star-Benedict-Cumberbatch-survived-kidnap-attempt-in-South-Africa.html |title= Sherlock star Benedict Cumberbatch survived kidnap attempt in South Africa |author= Donna Bowater |date= 2012-01-12 |publisher= The telegraph |language=  |accessdate=  |quote=  |archive-date= 2020-11-21 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20201121110400/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/tvandradio/9009080/Sherlock-star-Benedict-Cumberbatch-survived-kidnap-attempt-in-South-Africa.html |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref name="#2"/><ref name="#3"/>

=== 慈善工作及社會活動 ===
甘巴貝治是英國慈善組織《王子信托基金》（{{link-en| The Prince's Trust|The Prince's Trust}}）及英國運動神經元病協會（Motor Neurone Disease Association）的大使，曾多次參與這兩個組織相關的慈善活動，包括2012年《王子信托基金》的單車籌款<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.princes-trust.org.uk/about_the_trust/in_your_region/south_of_england/london_and_the_south_east/news/2012/1210_cumberbatch_bike_ride.aspx |title=Sherlock Star Saddles Up For The Prince's Trust |author= |date=2012-10 |publisher=The Prince's Trust |language= |accessdate= |quote= |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130130094858/http://www.princes-trust.org.uk/about_the_trust/in_your_region/south_of_england/london_and_the_south_east/news/2012/1210_cumberbatch_bike_ride.aspx |archivedate=2013-01-30 }}</ref>，以及為運動神經元病人（漸凍人）成立的生日募捐網站<ref>{{Cite web |url= http://web.alsa.org/site/TR?px=4109564&fr_id=10054&pg=personal#.VFDxDPmUfzP |title= Benedict Cumberbatch Birthday Fund |author= Debra Wu |date=  |publisher= The ALS Association |language=  |accessdate=  |quote=  |archive-date= 2014-09-09 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20140909001923/http://web.alsa.org/site/TR?px=4109564&fr_id=10054&pg=personal#.VFDxDPmUfzP |dead-url= no }}</ref>。2014年甘巴貝治接受為漸凍人募款的[[冰桶挑戰|冰桶挑戰]]活動，在長達2分鐘的片段中總共淋了6次冰水。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.express.co.uk/news/showbiz/502337/Benedict-Cumberbatch-does-the-ALS-Ice-Bucket-challenge-FIVE-times |title=Sherlock gets soaked! Benedict Cumberbatch does the ALS Ice Bucket challenge FIVE times |author=Kirsty McCormack |date=2014-08-22 |publisher=Daily Express |language= |accessdate= |quote= |archive-date=2015-04-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150407103547/http://www.express.co.uk/news/showbiz/502337/Benedict-Cumberbatch-does-the-ALS-Ice-Bucket-challenge-FIVE-times |dead-url=no }}</ref>甘巴貝治也曾多次捐贈自己的畫作及衣物義賣，為不同的慈善團體籌款。

甘巴貝治也活躍於體育界。2012年倫敦奧運會，甘巴貝治拍攝了一輯奧運宣傳短片，該短片於奧運開幕禮前播出<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.bbc.com/news/19022258 |title=Benedict Cumberbatch film starts London 2012 coverage |author= |date=2013-01-15 |publisher=BBC |language= |accessdate= |quote= |archive-date=2016-12-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161207073233/http://www.bbc.com/news/19022258 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2014年及2015年，甘巴貝治兩度獲邀為[[羅倫斯世界體育獎|羅倫斯世界體育獎]]頒獎禮擔任主持。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.laureus.com/news/benedict-cumberbatch-host-laureus-awards-ceremony |title=Benedict Cumberbatch to host Laureus Awards Ceremony |author= |date=2013-03-19 |publisher=The Independent |language= |accessdate= |quote= |archive-date=2016-04-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160424073217/https://www.laureus.com/news/benedict-cumberbatch-host-laureus-awards-ceremony |dead-url=no }}</ref>2014年，甘巴貝治先後出席了[[一級方程式賽車|一級方程式賽車]][[馬來西亞大獎賽|馬來西亞大獎賽]]及[[摩納哥大獎賽|摩納哥大獎賽]]，並兩次於頒獎禮上出任主持訪問獲獎車手。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/people/lewis-hamilton-wins-malaysian-gp-gets-interviewed-by-sherlock-star-benedict-cumberbatch-9224317.html |title=Lewis Hamilton wins Malaysian GP, gets interviewed by Sherlock star Benedict Cumberbatch |author=Tomas Jivanda |date=2013-03-30 |publisher=The Independent |language= |accessdate= |quote= |archive-date=2019-06-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190622172906/https://www.independent.co.uk/news/people/lewis-hamilton-wins-malaysian-gp-gets-interviewed-by-sherlock-star-benedict-cumberbatch-9224317.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2013年，甘巴貝治應邀擔任劍橋大學科學節（Cambridge Science Festival）的客席指導。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/showbiz/s129/sherlock/news/a452785/benedict-cumberbatch-to-guest-direct-cambridge-science-festival.html |title=Benedict Cumberbatch to guest direct Cambridge Science Festival |author=Tom Eames |date=2013-01-22 |publisher=Laureus World Sports Awards 2014 |language= |accessdate= |quote= |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924173637/http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/showbiz/s129/sherlock/news/a452785/benedict-cumberbatch-to-guest-direct-cambridge-science-festival.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

